  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients scheduled for colonoscopy with suspected large or multiple polys in the right
             colon

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  previous abdominal surgery

          -  history or currently diagnosed intra-abdominal cancer

          -  patients presenting with unstable angina

          -  drug abusers

          -  pregnant women

          -  patients with known colonic strictures
      </textblock>
